  refine ⟨T, hT, fun n ↦ ?_⟩
  by_contra hn; push_neg at hn
  suffices (1 / 2) ^ n ≤ P (⋂ k : ℕ, {ω | σ n k ω < min (τ n ω) (T n)}) by
    refine (by simp : ¬ (1 / 2 : ℝ≥0∞) ^ n ≤ 0) <| this.trans <| nonpos_iff_eq_zero.2 ?_
